    <stitle>No Idle APU/HVAC System - MAINTENANCE - Replacing Water Pump Belt</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="pm" graphiccount="2">
        <title>Replacing Water Pump Belt</title>
        <figure id="f1603719" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg16/g1603719.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="352px"
                     scalefitheight="352px"/>
            <caption>Figure 19. Replacing Water Pump Belt</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>To replace water pump belt, proceed as follows:</para>
        <seqlist style="arabic">
            <item>
                <para>Loosen tensioner nut using a 14mm wrench.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Remove 4 water pump pulley bolts using 10mm wrench.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Replace belt.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Tighten 4 water pump pulley bolts using 10mm torque wrench.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Tighten tensioner nut using a 14mm wrench.</para>
            </item>
        </seqlist>
        <figure id="f1603720" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg16/g1603720.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="152px"/>
            <caption>Figure 20. Belt Wear Determination</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
